hopobject.body: Will I have to work on Saturdays? amtec medical supplies Time to add Casey Kotchman to the list! The journeyman first baseman is our first baseball victim of 2013. Kotchman signed with the Miami Marlins and, shortly after he sustained a gash to his left index finger while trying to stop a pitching machine from hitting the ground after bumping into it. Said Kotchman: "I'm trying to be a gentleman to the machine." How'd that work out, CK?
